information: Urkraft Leinmanufaktur – your first port of call for 100% natural cold pressed linseed and linseed oil products for horses and dogs. Eiserbeck Naturprodukte UG guarantees the following for its linseed and linseed oil products: In-house manufacturing and filling, complete cold pressing below 40 °C, 100% food grade, no genetically modified raw materials (gmo-free), regular analyses of raw materials and the resulting end products. In our oil mill, we only press food grade linseed, without any additives, filter aids, flavour enhancers or preservatives. By using a special manufacturing and cold pressing process below 40 °C, our linseed products are extracted gently, which means that you as the end consumer can rest assured that all the important constituents of the linseed are retained in the end product and are made available to the body with optimum efficiency.
